<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُبْصِرًا}</span> ... مُضِيئًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَنَّى تُؤْفَكُونَ}</span> ... كَيْفَ تُصْرَفُونَ عَنِ الإِيمَانِ بِهِ؟!<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٦٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُؤْفَكُ}</span> ... يُصْرَفُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَبَارَكَ}</span> ... تَكَاثَرَ خَيْرُهُ وَفَضْلُهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنْ أُسْلِمَ}</span> ... أَنْ أَخْضَعَ وَأَنْقَادَ بِالطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَقَةٍ}</span> ... الدَّمِ الغَلِيظِ؛ المُتَعَلِّقِ بِجِدَارِ الرَّحِمِ، وَهُوَ أَحَدُ أَطْوَارِ الجَنِينِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِتَبْلُغُوا أَشُدَّكُمْ}</span> ... لِتَتَكَامَلَ قُوَّتُكُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَجَلًا مُّسَمًّى}</span> ... مُدَّةً مُقَدَّرَةً تَنْتَهِي بِهَا أَعْمَارُكُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنَّى يُصْرَفُونَ}</span> ... كَيْفَ يَعْدِلُونَ عَنْهَا مَعْ صِحَّتِهَا؟!<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالْكِتَابِ}</span> ... بِالقُرْآنِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالسَّلَاسِلُ}</span> ... القُيُودُ فِي الأَرْجُلِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْحَمِيمِ}</span> ... المَاءِ الَّذِي بَلَغَ غَايَةَ الحَرَارَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُسْجَرُونَ}</span> ... يُوقَدُ عَلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ضَلُّوا عَنَّا}</span> ... غَابُوا عَنْ عُيُونِنَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَمْرَحُونَ}</span> ... تَتَوَسَّعُونَ فيِ الفَرَحِ أَشَرًا وَبَطَرًا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَثْوَى}</span> ... مَاوَى، وَمَسْكَنُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُضِيَ بِالْحَقِّ}</span> ... حُكِمَ بِالعَدْلِ بَيْنَ الرُّسُلِ، وَمُكَذِّبِيهِمْ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>